Once upon a time there was an ant name- Rohit and a Grasshopper name- Grassy.
One day Grassy saw his friend Rohit and his Friends prserving the food to his house for Winter season
Grassy ask him why are you doing the work on this hot day come lets play.
Rohit said no winter season in coming at i want to prserve some food as you Know in winter season there is no food 
for us to eat.